fields.title: The Bennet Buttondown Shirt by Maeve: Striped Edition
fields.description: Tailored yet soft, Bennet is the star of the shirting world—it's perfect as the main feature, in a supporting role beneath your favorite jacket, or unbuttoned over a tank top.

fields.title: The Colette Cropped Wide-Leg Pants by Maeve
fields.description: Give a nod to mod with the Colette. Cropped with flare, our rave-reviewed silhouette charms with a form-fitting high rise and a breezy wide leg.

fields.title: The Tilda Maxi Slip Skirt
fields.description: If you haven't met the Tilda slip skirt, then bon jour! A French-inspired bias-cut design makes it drape and move just so – equally chic for a night out or a day about town.

fields.title: Mac Duggal Ruffled Cross-Back Smock-Waist Floral Embroidered Gown
fields.description: Whimsical ruffles and embroidered florals accent the V-neckline and criss-cross back of the Mac Duggal Cross-Back Smock-Waist Gown. Complete with ruffled trim and a smocked waist, this airy, maxi-length A-line silhouette is bursting with charm.
